responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "A0C4C587472B11D39A9E6EADF0FEDC2C", "Darling, Please meet me at Lotharia\'s Look, our special place. Oh! Who is fooling who. Tis everyone\'s special place. Yet, tis the place our lips first met. I will await you there. Our families may hold fast the quarrantine imposed by the Prime Helaer, but we cannot yield our love lest we combust in a fiery flash of passion.")
name: MIDD_0016_BRP_LoversNote_3
